rs\", however the place appears to be deserted.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 iLXgbm\" data-component=\"advertisement-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 fAzFNb\"><div class=\"sc-66bf5539-1 bJFWOK\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" data-testid=\"ad-unit\"><div class=\"dotcom-ad\" data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_3\" id=\"dotcom-mid_3\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 hoFfRa\" data-component=\"image-block\"><figure class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 laOREU\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gmICnp\"><div class=\"sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV\" data-testid=\"image\"><img aria-label=\"image unavailable\" class=\"sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script\" src=\"https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260220-084609-e0c5de56b9-web-2.40.1-3/grey-placeholder.png\"/><img alt=\"Screen Burn/Konami/Annapurna Video game graphic of a smoky harbour with a life ring and stairs leading up to a higher platform\" class=\"sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/33a1/live/ac34a8e0-0b1f-11f1-a204-b3f033b84443.jpg.webp 1536w\"/><span class=\"sc-5340b511-2 jVqbAn\">Screen Burn/Konami/Annapurna</span></div></div><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gmICnp\"><figcaption class=\"sc-536eff7b-0 gnQokQ\">The developers said they wanted the setting to feel isolated </figcaption></div></figure></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">Screen Burn co-founder Jon McKellan said the team were keen to bring a new setting to the popular series.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">In a recent transmission on the Silent Hill YouTube channel, he said they originally planned to keep the location vaguely in northern Europe.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">But he added: \"There was a drive to create something that felt authentic to us and it kind of felt natural to bring it home.\"</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 iLXgbm\" data-component=\"advertisement-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 fAzFNb\"><div class=\"sc-66bf5539-1 bJFWOK\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" data-testid=\"ad-unit\"><div class=\"dotcom-ad\" data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_4\" id=\"dotcom-mid_4\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 hoFfRa\" data-component=\"links-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gmICnp\"><div class=\"sc-666b6d83-0 sc-c4fb5674-0 jYmMqa doYqeg\"><span class=\"sc-c4fb5674-2 bBuHEW\" data-testid=\"links-title\">Stories you may have missed</span><div class=\"sc-666b6d83-0 sc-c4fb5674-1 gEjRXC jkjVgq\" data-testid=\"links-grid\"><div class=\"sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx\" data-indexcard=\"true\" data-testid=\"chester-card\"><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi\" data-testid=\"external-anchor\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c24g1jyl3vmo\" target=\"_self\"><div class=\"sc-cf565bcc-0 kwPVOm\" data-testid=\"chester-article\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK\"><h2 class=\"sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa\" data-testid=\"card-headline\">Female athletes hit back at 'weird' and 'derogatory' comments about their appearance</h2></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class=\"sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx\" data-indexcard=\"true\" data-testid=\"chester-card\"><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi\" data-testid=\"external-anchor\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cn9e32yv9g5o\" target=\"_self\"><div class=\"sc-cf565bcc-0 kwPVOm\" data-testid=\"chester-article\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK\"><h2 class=\"sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa\" data-testid=\"card-headline\">Delivery van 'stuck on deadliest mudflat footpath'</h2></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class=\"sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx\" data-indexcard=\"true\" data-testid=\"chester-card\"><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi\" data-testid=\"external-anchor\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cddn0n3p2ppo\" target=\"_self\"><div class=\"sc-cf565bcc-0 kwPVOm\" data-testid=\"chester-article\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK\"><h2 class=\"sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa\" data-testid=\"card-headline\">What is behind spike in pothole related call-outs?</h2></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">McKellan said he was wanted to use the location to help tell the story, and his team studied the village's features to bring it to life in the world of Silent Hill.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">\"It's the smell and the wind and the sound of the place, all of that together is what you're trying to recreate,\" he said.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">\"When I started to write the story about what this town was, what happened to this town, the isolation was a big factor. </p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">\"There's like an existential dread that comes with that. Silent Hill has always had a sense of not being able to leave the town, and face why you're there.\"</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">He said recreating the haar accurately and how it obscures things from the player was a key part of this.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 iLXgbm\" data-component=\"advertisement-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 fAzFNb\"><div class=\"sc-66bf5539-1 bJFWOK\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" data-testid=\"ad-unit\"><div class=\"dotcom-ad\" data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_5\" id=\"dotcom-mid_5\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 hoFfRa\" data-component=\"image-block\"><figure class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 laOREU\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gmICnp\"><div class=\"sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV\" data-testid=\"image\"><img aria-label=\"image unavailable\" class=\"sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script\" src=\"https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260220-084609-e0c5de56b9-web-2.40.1-3/grey-placeholder.png\"/><img alt=\"Screen Burn/Konami/Annapurna Video game graphic of a narrow street in fog with bunting and a lamppost dimly lighting the alleyway\" class=\"sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/fefe/live/76ba0430-0b1f-11f1-b2d9-a9bd89759413.jpg.webp 1536w\"/><span class=\"sc-5340b511-2 jVqbAn\">Screen Burn/Konami/Annapurna</span></div></div><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gmICnp\"><figcaption class=\"sc-536eff7b-0 gnQokQ\">The winding alleyways in Silent Hill: Townfall mimic similar features in St Monans</figcaption></div></figure></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">Art director Paul Abbott said the misty environment in the game reminded him of early morning walks to school when he was growing up in a small fishing village.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">\"It's a beautifully epic, grey, drizzly environment and we're bringing that to the game,\" he said.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">He said the team had painstakingly recreated recognisable elements of the town, such as the winding alleyways and the texture of the piers.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">McKellan said it was a \"genuine honour\" to work with and contribute to the franchise.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">\"It's not an opportunity we ever thought we'd get, but it's one we knew we all wanted right away,\" he added.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 lmzibM\" data-component=\"text-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 IAFLu\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\">The game will be released later in 2026.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 iLXgbm\" data-component=\"advertisement-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 fAzFNb\"><div class=\"sc-66bf5539-1 bJFWOK\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" data-testid=\"ad-unit\"><div class=\"dotcom-ad\" data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_6\" id=\"dotcom-mid_6\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 hoFfRa\" data-component=\"links-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gmICnp\"><div class=\"sc-666b6d83-0 sc-c4fb5674-0 jYmMqa doYqeg\"><div class=\"sc-666b6d83-0 sc-c4fb5674-1 gEjRXC jkjVgq\" data-testid=\"links-grid\"><div class=\"sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx\" data-indexcard=\"true\" data-testid=\"chester-card\"><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi\" data-testid=\"external-anchor\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c0335ljkg5ro\" target=\"_self\"><div class=\"sc-cf565bcc-0 kwPVOm\" data-testid=\"chester-article\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK\"><h2 class=\"sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa\" data-testid=\"card-headline\">I almost died trying to get salt from the sea</h2></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class=\"sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx\" data-indexcard=\"true\" data-testid=\"chester-card\"><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi\" data-testid=\"external-anchor\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cx2nr219xk0o\" target=\"_self\"><div class=\"sc-cf565bcc-0 kwPVOm\" data-testid=\"chester-article\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP\"><div class=\"sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK\"><h2 class=\"sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa\" data-testid=\"card-headline\">Why does GTA 6 keep getting delayed?</h2></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 iLXgbm\" data-component=\"advertisement-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 fAzFNb\"><div class=\"sc-66bf5539-1 bJFWOK\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" data-testid=\"ad-unit\"><div class=\"dotcom-ad\" data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_7\" id=\"dotcom-mid_7\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"sc-9cd5bb24-0 hoFfRa\" data-component=\"tag-list-block\"><div class=\"sc-cd6075cf-0 DQtHs\"><div class=\"sc-82b3c53b-0 gDQlgg\"><div class=\"sc-6bf80075-0 lllwyY\"><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-57521d02-0 jsVxCb\" data-testid=\"internal-link\" href=\"/news/topics/c008ql15vdxt\">Gaming</a></div><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-57521d02-0 jsVxCb\" data-testid=\"internal-link\" href=\"/news/topics/c0n168gw8dpt\">St Monance</a></div><div data-testid=\"anchor-inner-wrapper\"><a class=\"sc-57521d02-0 jsVxCb\" data-testid=\"internal-link\" href=\"/news/scotland\">Scotland</a></div></div></div></div></div></article>",
